  skullRemark: Hehe, tricky one to judge, huh?
  luciferRemark: 'Money and life - shall we weigh them on the same moral scale?

    

    (Pause.)

    

    Three
    lives saved. One life lost to greed. What''s the exchange rate?

    

    He
    had a chance to be something better. For one brief moment, he was. And then...

    

    (Soft
    laugh.)

    

    Old habits.'
